      "description": "This car is in fair condition. It runs and drives, but has noticeable wear on both the interior and exterior. There are some minor mechanical issues that should be addressed, along with cosmetic blemishes and general signs of age and use. Suitable for a buyer comfortable with a vehicle that needs some attention.",
