    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project car or a fixer-upper with potential? This vehicle runs and drives, giving you a solid starting point for repairs or parts use. It's in poor condition \u2014 you can expect notable mechanical issues and visible cosmetic wear that will need real attention. But if you're handy or looking for an affordable entry point, this could be a rewarding opportunity at a great price!",
